# gold.dim_products

## Purpose

The **dim_products** table is a **dimension table** that stores descriptive information about products.
It allows business users to analyze sales performance across different **product categories, subcategories, and product lines**.

## Columns

| Column Name    | Data Type    | Description                                                            |
| -------------- | ------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Product_Key    | BIGINT       | Surrogate key uniquely identifying each product in the dimension table |
| Product_id     | INT          | Original product identifier from the source system                     |
| Product_Number | NVARCHAR(50) | Unique product number used for product identification                  |
| Product_Name   | NVARCHAR(50) | Name of the product                                                    |
| Category_id    | NVARCHAR(50) | Identifier for the product category                                    |
| Category       | NVARCHAR(50) | Category to which the product belongs                                  |
| Subcategory    | NVARCHAR(50) | Subcategory of the product                                             |
| maintenance    | NVARCHAR(50) | Maintenance classification of the product                              |
| Cost           | INT          | Cost associated with producing or acquiring the product                |
| Product_Line   | NVARCHAR(50) | Product line classification                                            |
| Start_Date     | DATE         | Date when the product became available or active                       |

---

# gold.fact_sales

## Purpose

The **fact_sales** table is a **fact table** that stores transactional sales data.
It records each sales transaction and links to the **customer and product dimension tables** using surrogate keys. This table is used for analyzing **sales performance, revenue, order quantities, and pricing**.

## Columns

| Column Name   | Data Type    | Description                                                    |
| ------------- | ------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Order_Number  | NVARCHAR(50) | Unique identifier for each sales order                         |
| product_key   | BIGINT       | Foreign key referencing the product in the product dimension   |
| Customer_Key  | BIGINT       | Foreign key referencing the customer in the customer dimension |
| Order_Date    | DATE         | Date when the order was placed                                 |
| Shipping_date | DATE         | Date when the order was shipped                                |
| Due_Date      | DATE         | Expected delivery date for the order                           |
| Sales_amount  | INT          | Total sales amount for the order                               |
| Quantity      | INT          | Number of product units sold                                   |
| sls_price     | INT          | Price per unit of the product sold                             |

